infodynamics.measures.continuous.kernel
Class KernelEstimatorUniVariate

java.lang.Object
  infodynamics.measures.continuous.kernel.KernelEstimatorUniVariate

public class KernelEstimatorUniVariate
extends java.lang.Object

Class to maintain probability distribution function for a single variable, using kernel estimates.

For more details on kernel estimation for computing probability distribution functions, see Kantz and Schreiber (below).

Author:
Joseph Lizier, joseph.lizier at gmail.com
See Also:
"H. Kantz and T. Schreiber, 'Nonlinear Time Series Analysis'. Cambridge, MA: Cambridge University Press, 1997"
